/**
 * Python bindings and test scaffolding for projects using the recommended [XSMP-SDK](https://github.com/ThalesGroup/xsmp-sdk) profile.
 *
 * This tool is designed to work with `profile 'xsmp-sdk'` and follows the XSMP SDK workflow for generated Python support and Python-based tests.
 *
 * Documentation:
 * - [XSMP-SDK Quickstart](https://thalesgroup.github.io/xsmp-sdk/quickstart.html)
 * - [XSMP-SDK Repository](https://github.com/ThalesGroup/xsmp-sdk)
 */
tool 'python'
